cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.NE 

The paper discusses reinforcement learning algorithms and their performance in high-dimensional domains with continuous action spaces. This falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of the Mujoco robotics simulator suggests a focus on robotics (cs.RO) and systems and control (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper proposes a novel algorithm for actor-critic learning, which is a type of neural network architecture commonly used in reinforcement learning, indicating a focus on neural networks (cs.NE).
